<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About</title>
    <style>
        * {
            padding: 0;
            margin: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: sans-serif;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        ::-webkit-scrollbar {
            width: 10px;
        }

        ::-webkit-scrollbar-track {
            box-shadow: inset 0 0 5px grey;
        }

        ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
            background: #1bbc96;
        }

        ::selection {
            background: none;
        }

        body {
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        a {
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 500;
            font-size: 20px;
        }

        .about {
            position: absolute;
            left: 0%;
            top: 0%;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.09);
            width: 55vw;
            z-index: 1000;
            padding: 10vh 8% 5vh 8%;
        }

        .about h1 {
            color: white;
            font-size: 80px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .bubbleBuster {
            width: 250px;
            height: 70px;
            padding-left: 8px;
            padding-right: 8px;
            background: #1bbc96;
            color:  #121212;
            border-radius: 14px;
            font-size: 30px;
            font-weight: 600;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .about p {
            margin-top: 8vh;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: white;
            line-height: 30px;
        }

        .links {
            line-height: 25px;
            margin-top: 10vh;
        }

        .bubble-img {
            position: absolute;
            top: 15%;
            right: 35%;
            transition: 600ms;
        }

        .help {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 5vh;
            right: 28%;
            z-index: 1001;
            transition: 500ms ease-in;
        }

        .game {
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            border-radius: 50%;
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 6%;
            right: 52%;
            z-index: 1001;
            transition: 500ms ease-in;
        }

        .help:hover, .game:hover {
            transform: scale(1.1);
        }

        .user {
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 1000px #11a582;
            transition: 600ms ease-in-out;
        }

        .user-bg {
            display: none;
            transition: 3000ms;
            opacity: 0;
            z-index: 1002;
            position: absolute;
            right: 0%;
            transform: translateY(-20%);
            padding-top: 100px;
            transition: 1000ms ease-in-out;
        }
        
        .log {
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            color: white;
            display: none;
            font-weight: 500;
            font-size: large;
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            left: 30%;
            z-index: 1003;
        }

        form input:focus {
            outline: none;
        }
        form input {
            width: 250px;
            height: 40px;
            padding: 5px;
            border: 5px solid #1bbc96;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin: 10px;
        }

        .data-form {
            display: none;
            position: absolute;
            top: 30%;
            right: 18%;
            z-index: 1004;
        }

        .submit {
            background: #1bbc96;
            color: white;
            height: 40px;
            transition: 400ms;
        }

        .back {
            width: fit-content;
            color: white;
            display: none;
            font-weight: 900;
            margin-left: 50px;
            font-size: 30px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: 400ms;
            position: fixed;
            top: 3%;
        }

        .submit:hover {
            border: 4px solid white;
        }

        .back:hover {
            transform: scale(1.08);
            border-bottom: 6px solid black;
        }

        #login {
            cursor: pointer;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body onload="ready()">

    <canvas></canvas>

    <div class="about">

        <div class="bubble-img"><img src="assets/images/about bubble.png" alt=""></div>
        <h1>About</h1>

        <div class="bubbleBuster">Bubble Buster</div>

        <p>Bubble buster is a  multiplayer or solo fun 
        browser game made as a project for learning 
        purpose. This game can be played in teams of five 
        and can be enjoyed online. This is a browser 
        game which means you dont have to install it in your
        system only requirements are good internet 
        connection, some good friends and your PC.
        As this is built for learning purpose  it is not available
        for mobile right now but we are working on it and soon 
        you will have it on your phones too.Support us, hire us
        give some feedbacks.  To start game click on
        Bubble Buster to know about controls or other stuff
        click on Help. Enjoyyyy!!!
        <br>
        God bless you :)</p>

        <div class="links">
            <a href="#" style="color: #1bbc96;"><b>Support Us</b></a><br>
            <a href="https://elegant-ritchie-960760.netlify.app/" style="color: #1bbc96;"><b>Hire Us At Nukers</b></a><br>
            <a href="#" style="color: #1bbc96;"><b>Feedback</b></a>
        </div>

        <div class="help"><img src="assets/images/about-help.png" alt=""></div>

    </div>

    <div class="game"><img src="assets/images/bubble-buster.png" alt=""></div>

    <div class="user-bg"><img src="assets/images/Group 61 (6).png" alt=""></div>

    <div class="log"><span id="change">Multiplayer </span><span id="login" style="border-bottom: 2px solid #1bbc96; color: #1bbc96;">mode</span></div>

    <div class="back">Back</div>
    <div class="data-form">
        <form action="/menu" method="POST">
            <input id="name" type="text" name="roomname" placeholder="Enter room" autocomplete="off"><br>
            <input type="text" name="username" placeholder="username" autocomplete="off" required><br>
            <input class="submit" type="submit" value="let's go">
        </form>
    </div>
</body>
</html>

